      "pos": [
        2759,
        2788
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "What tools do I use to create a VNet?",
      "pos": [
        2794,
        2831
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "You can use the following tools to create or configure a virtual network:",
      "pos": [
        2833,
        2906
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "You can use the Management Portal.",
      "pos": [
        2910,
        2944
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "See <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>How to manage Virtual Network (VNet) Properties<ept id=\"p1\">](virtual-networks-settings.md)</ept>.",
      "pos": [
        2945,
        3029
      ]
    },
