      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "You can specify DNS server IP addresses in the VNet settings.",
      "pos": [
        6928,
        6989
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "This will be applied as the default DNS server(s) for all VMs in the VNet.",
      "pos": [
        6990,
        7064
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "How many DNS servers can I specify?",
      "pos": [
